sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Passenger
    participant UI as React UI
    participant API as API Client
    participant BE as Express Backend
    participant RideC as Ride Controller
    participant BookC as Booking Controller
    participant PayC as Payment Controller
    participant Mongo as MongoDB Atlas
    participant Razorpay as Razorpay
    actor Driver

    Passenger->>UI: Search rides
    UI->>API: GET /api/rides/search?source&destination
    API->>BE: search request
    BE->>RideC: searchRides()
    RideC->>Mongo: Find rides with seatsAvailable > 0
    Mongo-->>RideC: Matching ride documents
    RideC-->>BE: Filtered rides by route order
    BE-->>API: Ride list
    API-->>UI: Render ride cards

    Passenger->>UI: Request seat
    UI->>API: POST /api/bookings/request
    API->>BE: requestBooking(rideId, passengerId)
    BE->>BookC: requestBooking()
    BookC->>Mongo: Validate ride + passenger + duplicates
    Mongo-->>BookC: OK
    BookC->>Mongo: Insert Booking(status=REQUESTED)
    Mongo-->>BookC: Booking created
    BookC-->>BE: Booking response
    BE-->>API: REQUESTED booking
    API-->>UI: Show request sent

    Driver->>UI: Open bookings page
    UI->>API: GET /api/bookings/incoming?driverId
    API->>BE: incoming bookings request
    BE->>BookC: getIncomingBookings()
    BookC->>Mongo: Query bookings for driver's rides
    Mongo-->>BookC: Incoming bookings
    BookC-->>BE: Booking list
    BE-->>API: Incoming requests
    API-->>UI: Show incoming requests

    Driver->>UI: Accept booking
    UI->>API: POST /api/bookings/:id/accept
    API->>BE: acceptBooking(bookingId, driverId)
    BE->>BookC: acceptBooking()
    BookC->>Mongo: Validate ownership + seatsAvailable
    Mongo-->>BookC: OK
    BookC->>Mongo: Decrement Ride.seatsAvailable
    BookC->>Mongo: Update Booking.status = ACCEPTED
    Mongo-->>BookC: Updated ride and booking
    BookC-->>BE: ACCEPTED booking
    BE-->>API: Accepted response
    API-->>UI: Enable payment CTA

    Passenger->>UI: Open payment page
    UI->>API: POST /api/payments/intent
    API->>BE: createOrder(bookingId)
    BE->>PayC: createOrder()
    PayC->>Mongo: Validate Booking.status == ACCEPTED
    Mongo-->>PayC: Booking + ride data
    PayC->>Razorpay: Create order(amount, receipt)
    Razorpay-->>PayC: orderId
    PayC->>Mongo: Upsert Payment(status=CREATED)
    Mongo-->>PayC: Payment saved
    PayC-->>BE: orderId + keyId + amount
    BE-->>API: Payment init response
    API-->>UI: Open Razorpay Checkout

    Passenger->>Razorpay: Complete test payment
    Razorpay-->>UI: razorpay_payment_id + razorpay_order_id
    UI->>API: POST /api/payments/:id/confirm
    API->>BE: paymentSuccess(orderId, paymentId)
    BE->>PayC: paymentSuccess()
    PayC->>Mongo: Find payment by orderId
    Mongo-->>PayC: Payment + booking
    PayC->>Mongo: Update Payment.status = PAID
    PayC->>Mongo: Update Booking.status = PAID
    Mongo-->>PayC: Saved
    PayC-->>BE: Payment recorded
    BE-->>API: Success response
    API-->>UI: Redirect to /bookings

    alt Passenger cancels before 24h window closes
        Passenger->>UI: Cancel ride
        UI->>API: POST /api/bookings/:id/cancel
        API->>BE: cancelBooking(bookingId, passengerId)
        BE->>BookC: cancelBooking()
        BookC->>Mongo: Validate passenger + hoursUntilRide >= 24
        Mongo-->>BookC: Booking + ride + payment
        BookC->>Mongo: Update Booking.status = CANCELLED
        BookC->>Mongo: Restore seat if previously accepted/paid
        opt Booking was PAID
            BookC->>Mongo: Update Payment.status = REFUND_INITIATED
        end
        Mongo-->>BookC: Cancellation persisted
        BookC-->>BE: cancellation response + support email
        BE-->>API: Cancellation confirmed
        API-->>UI: Show refund/support alert
    else Ride starts within 24h
        BookC-->>BE: 400 Cannot cancel within 24 hours
        BE-->>API: Error response
        API-->>UI: Show cancellation locked message
    end
